channel.title: Project, int[] tomsProject;
channel.description:
[u]Introuduction - int[] TomsProject;[/u]
Hey, welcome to my new project, this is based of final devolution, a Runescape econmy based server, which includes quests, and unique qualities. The name, i got bored of boring names, so i decided to add a Java twist to the name!
[u]Features - int[] TomsProject;[/u]
[ul][li]Fully working npc dialouge for Lumbridge guide.[/li][li]70% fully working woodcutting, with all correct logs, and runescape style xp.[/li][li]Basic fletching, only work for logs up to willow at the moment, will be updates.[/li][li]Brilliant econmy, Runescape style drops, no shops that sell any armour above adamant, nor wepons, all Npc drops.[/li][li]95% Runescape Npc hitpoints.[/li][li]Prepared server for highscores, My SQL.[/li][li]1 fully working quest, another being added later in development.[/li][li]Fully working npc areas, i.e Lumbridge goblins, near Al-Kharid gate, all Npcs move.[/li][li]You need 10 gp to get in to Al-Kharid, via gate.[/li][li]Npc dialougue to get throught gate.[/li][li]Added theiving stalls, in Draynor, you get a small amount of runes.[/li][li]fully working willows on Draynor.[/li][li]Fully working thieving levels for stalls, and Npcs.[/li][li]Thieving timers 70% done.[/li][li]Woodcutting timers 60% done.[/li][li]Censors on client, for swearing, ect..[/li][li]Fully working censors for no-ip, ect..[/li][li]10% Firemaking, being developed on, drops ashes after fire is out.[/li][li]Random events, 0%, im looking at adding them further in development.[/li][li]IPmanager, glitches solved.[/li][li]No thread per client[/li][li]Low CPU usage, thanks killames.[/li][li]2% clue scrolls, there only being dropped of Goblins, and it doesn't actually give you the clue yet or tell you what to do yet.[/li][li]Premium, 10% done, premium wepons, that are non-tradable, and some tradabale. And there is currently 1 premium training zone. And i look to add 1 premium quest.[/li][li]You now choose a God, yes i know it was a tutorial, but i made it link up to a cape which you can wear depending on the God you choose.[/li][li]Mage bank, is premium only.[/li][li]1% farming, just added seed drops, and will add a farming shop, that sells buckets, watering cans ect soon.[/li][li]Fully working cows outside Lumbridge, they drop cowhides, and bones, i will add raw beef, when cooking is added.[/li][/ul]
[u]Pictures -int[] TomsProject;[/[/u]

[img]http://i293.photobucket.com/albums/mm78/5frtgvhy/THISONE5.jpg[/img]
[u]Ending - int[] TomsProject;[/u]
I will add more pictures of Cows, more dialougue later + update the features, please post back your comments and possible suggestions, thanks, Tom.
- int[] TomsProject;
[u]BETS TESTING APPLICATION - Project, int[] TomsProject;[/u]
Hello, this is the BETA testing side, i need 5 BETA testers, who are active, matture, and willing to help, only a few out of thoose who apply will be accepted.
Application:
[code]Name: How active are you?: Email adress?: Any other infomation?: [/code]
Goodluck.
